column26:
Description:

After selecting the Image and clicking on edit tab admin should be able to see required fields marked with asterisk sign.

steps to reproduce:

# Open the browser.
# Enter the Real Estate URL.
# Login page appears on the screen.
# Enter Username and Password.
# Click on sign in tab.
# Real Estate webpage appears on the screen.
# Go to the media section.
# Media library will appear.
# Click on edit option.
# Caption, Alternative text, Description, File type, File size, File name, File URL fields will appear.
# Required fields does not contain asterisk sign next to it.



Expected Result:

Mandatory fields should contain asterisk sign next to them.



Actual Result:

Mandatory fields does not contain asterisk sign.



!image-20210906-072650.png|width=1334,height=686!

Check for autosuggestions in 'Search Media Items' field for new search
column26:
Description:

When an admin login the real estate application and searches for new items then he or she would be able to get the autosuggestions for easily accessing the files.



Steps to reproduce:

# Open the browser.
# Enter the Real Estate URL.
# Login page appears on the screen.
# Enter Username and Password.
# Click on sign in tab.
# Real Estate webpage appears on the screen.
# Go to the media section.
# Media library will appear.
# Go to the ‘search media items’ field available on the screen.
# Click on 'search media item' field and enter initial letter of picture title which is not previously searched.
# Autosuggestions will not appear for new search.
# click on enter tab.



Expected Result:

After entering data in the ‘Search Media Items’ section, autosuggestions should appear.



Actual Result:

Autosuggestions are not appearing in the ‘Search Media Items’ area.

!image-20210905-143900.png|width=319,height=99!

!image-20210905-145026.png|width=306,height=82!
